category>俄罗斯</category><category>弗拉基米尔普京</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>战争与冲突</category><category>外交</category><category>G7</category><category>乌克兰战争：巴西卢拉拒绝普京访问俄罗斯的邀请</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Can the EU’s infrastructure initiative be a better, greener version of China’s belt and road?]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p>在 5 月 13 日于斯德哥尔摩举行的欧盟印太部长级论坛上，欧盟重申致力于通过其<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3158090/eu-launches-infrastructure-drive-true-alternative-chinas-belt-and-road?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221517_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="decb87a4-a0db-4a54-b968-79b742de0b0c" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">全球门户倡议</a>加强与印太地区的联系与合作。欧洲计划对该地区的基础设施发展进行战略投资，2023 年及以后将启动 20 多个旗舰项目。</p><p>仅仅六天后，习近平主席与哈萨克斯坦、吉尔吉斯斯坦、塔吉克斯坦、土库曼斯坦和乌兹别克斯坦领导人主持了首次<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3221093/china-can-help-central-asian-brethren-unite-xi-jinping-tells-xian-summit?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221517_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="3a061e62-3895-4035-a515-6236413474f4" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">中国－中亚领导人会晤</a>。 “一带一路”倡议提出以来，中国与中亚五国贸易增长迅速，去年达到702亿美元，同比增长40%。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .207